Class Summary 
Class Description
GameListener
GameListener monitors keystrokes during the soccer game
GameMenuBar
Represents the menu bar for the game
GamePanel
GamePanel is the panel to display the game
GamePlayer
The GamePlayer class represents a soccer player in the game.
Goalkeeper
The Goalkeeper class represents a GamePlayer that is a goalkeeper.
MenubarListener
MenubarListener monitors the menu bar to control the game
MiniSoccerApp
MiniSoccerApp is a mini soccer game.
PlayerCollection
An iterable Collection of GamePlayers
PlayerFactory
A factory class for GamePlayers
PlayerStatistics
This class is a representation of a player's statistics.
SoccerBall
The SoccerBall class represents a soccerball
SoccerGame
SoccerGame represents the soccer game
Striker
The Striker class represents a GamePlayer that is a striker.
